          {
            "text": "A short energy statement from Day 33 of the MONEY program. The release addresses the checking-for-the-catch reflex; the allow opens room to receive surprise money without the immediate search for what's wrong with it.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
